General Repair - General Repair:
Doors & Galles > Front Doors
Qher
The door looks like someone tried to kick it in. Part of the framing around the glass is busted. Not sure if it can be repaired or if it needs to be replaced. We will
install (1) new metal door and frame.
Assessment :
"We armed on site and placed a board over the hole. We will install (1) new metal door and frame.
Scope: 181 Trip
Secure work area
Measure hole in door
Cut plywood to ft
Secure plywood to door for board up
Clean work area
Dispose of any debris offsite
In shop hours
Scope: Door replacement- lead time: 2-3 weeks
Source and obtain materials
Secure work asa
Disconnect and remove door from hinges
Relocate damaged door for disposal
Remove top hinge
Remove bottom hinge
Remove framing
Remove side-light and glass
Install new side-light and glass
Install new framing
Dril new pilot holes for new hinges
Install new top hinge
Install new bottom hinge
Assemble door hardware
Install (1) new metal door onto hinges
Align hinges as needed to dose property
Function test
Clean work arca
Dispose of any debris off site
"Work to be performed DURING normal business hours
Total
